# GrandPrize and ETH Price

- [`GrandPrize.tsx`](mdc:src/components/GrandPrize.tsx): Displays the current grand prize in the PoolTogether protocol, both in the prize token and its USD equivalent.
  - Fetches prize pool and token data using hooks from `@generationsoftware/hyperstructure-react-hooks`.
  - Uses [`useEthPriceInUsd`](mdc:src/hooks/useEthPrice.tsx) to fetch the current ETH price in USD for display.
  - Shows loading states using [`Loading.tsx`](mdc:src/components/Loading.tsx).

- [`useEthPrice.tsx`](mdc:src/hooks/useEthPrice.tsx): Custom React hook to fetch the price of ETH in USD using token price data from the PoolTogether SDK.
